quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Yaqeenan falaah payi hai iman laney walon ne jo
  23,2,Apni namaz mein khushu ikhtiyar karte hain (Salat with humility)
  23,3,Laghviyat (vain things) se door rehte hain
  23,4,Zakaat ke tareeqe par aamil hotey hain
  23,5,Apni sharmgaahon ki hifazat karte hain
  23,6,Siwaye apni biwiyon ke aur un auraton ke jo unki milk e yameen mein hon (right hand posseses) ke unpar (mehfooz na rakhne mein) woh qabil e malamat nahin hain
  23,7,Albatta jo uske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi zyadati karne waley hain
  23,8,Apni amanaton (trusts) aur apne ahad o paiman (promises) ka paas rakhte hain
  23,9,Aur apni namazon ki muhafizat (hifazat) karte hain
  23,10,Yahi log woh waris hain
  23,11,Jo miraas mein firdous payenge aur usmein hamesha rahenge
  23,12,Humne Insaan ko mitti ke saatt (essence of clay) se banaya
  23,13,Phir usey ek mehfooz jaga tapki hui boondh mein tabdeel kiya
  23,14,"Phir us boondh ko lothday ki shakal di, phir lothday ko boti bana diya, phir boti ki haddiyan (bones) banayin, phir haddiyon par gosht chadhaya. Phir usey ek dusri hi makhlooq bana khada kiya. Pas bada hi ba-barakat hai Allah, sab karigaron se accha kaarigar(creator)"
  23,15,Phir iske baad tumko zaroor marna hai
  23,16,Phir qayamat ke roz yaqeenan tum uthaye jaogey
  23,17,"Aur tumhare upar humne saat (seven) raastey banaye, takhleeq ke kaam se hum kuch na-balad na thay (We are never unmindful of (our) Creation"
  23,18,Aur aasmaan se humne theek hisaab ke mutabiq ek khaas miqdar mein pani utara aur usko zameen mein thehara diya. Hum usey jis tarah chahein gayab kar sakte hain
  23,19,"Phir is pani ke zariye se humne tumhare liye khajoor aur angoor ke baagh paida kardiye, tumhare liye in baaghon mein bahut se lazeez phal hain aur unsey tum rozi haasil karte ho"
  23,20,"Aur woh darakht bhi humne paida kiya jo Tur-e-seena (mount sinai) se nikalta hai, teil (oil) bhi liye huey ugta hai aur khane walon ke liye saalan bhi"
  23,21,"Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhare liye maweshiyon mein bhi ek sabaq hai unke paithon (bellies) mein jo kuch hai usi mein se ek cheez hum tumhein pilatey hain, aur tumhare liye unmein bahut se dusre faiyde bhi hain"
  23,22,Unko tum khate ho aur unpar aur kashtiyon par sawaar bhi kiye jatey ho
  23,23,"Humne Nooh ko uski qaum ki taraf bheja, usne kaha “ aey meri qaum ke logon, Allah ki bandagi karo, uske siwa tumhare liye koi aur mabood nahin hai, kya tum darte nahin ho?”"
  23,24,Uski qaum ke jin sardaaron ne maanne se inkar kiya woh kehne lagey ke “yeh shaks kuch nahin hai magar ek bashar(Insaan) tum hi jaisa. Iski garz yeh hai ke tumpar bartari (superiority) haasil karey. Allah ko agar bhejna hota to farishtey bhejta.Yeh baat to humne kabhi apne baap dada ke waqton mein suni hi nahin ( ke bashar Rasool bankar aaye)
  23,25,"Kuch nahin , bas is aadmi ko zara junoon lahaq(possessed) ho gaya hai, kuch muddat aur dekhlo [ ( shayad ifaqa ho jaaye)( may be he is cured)]”"
  23,26,"Nooh ne kaha “parwardigar, in logon ne jo meri takzeeb ki hai ispar ab tu hi meri nusrat farma.”"
  23,27,"Humne uspar wahee ki ke “hamari nigrani mein aur hamari wahee ke mutabiq kashti (ark) tayyar kar. Phir jab hamara hukum aa jaye aur tannur ubal paday to har qisam ke jaanwaron mein se ek ek joda lekar usmein sawaar ho ja, aur apne ehal o ayaal ko bhi saath le, siwai unke jinke khilaf pehle faisla ho chuka hai, aur zaalimon ke maamle mein mujhse kuch na kehna, yeh ab garq (doob/ drown) honay waley hain"
  23,28,"Phir jab tu apne saathiyon sameth kashti par sawar ho jaye to keh, shukar hai us khuda ka jisne humein zaalim logon se nijaat di"
  23,29,"Aur keh, parwardigar, mujhko barakat wali jagah utaar aur tu behtareen jagah dene wala hai.”"
  23,30,Is qissey mein badi nishaniyan hain aur aazmaish to hum karke hi rehte hain
  23,31,Inke baad humne ek dusre daur ki qaum uthayi
  23,32,"Phir un mein khud unhi ki qaum ka ek Rasool bheja ( jisne unhein dawat di) ke Allah ki bandagi karo, tumhare liye uske siwa koi aur maabood nahin hai, kya tum darte nahin ho"
  23,33,"Uski qaum ke jin sardaron ne maanne se inkar kiya aur aakhirat ki peshi ko jhutlaya, jinko humne duniya ki zindagi mein aasuda kar rakkha tha, woh kehne lagey “ye shaks kuch nahin hai magar ek bashar tum hi jaisa, jo kuch tum khate ho wahi yeh khata hai aur jo kuch tum peete ho wahi yeh peeta hai"
  23,34,Ab agar tumne apne hi jaise ek bashar ki itaat qabool karli to tum ghatay hi mein rahey
  23,35,Yeh tumhein ittila deta hai ke jab tum mar kar mitti ho jaogey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jaogey us waqt tum (qabaron se) nikale jaogey